<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Rideau Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Rideau Park is a residential community nestled in the crescent-shaped land formed by the
                curve of Elbow River in the southwest quadrant of Calgary, Alberta.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The 4th Street SW runs along the eastern border, with the Elbow River covering all the
                other three borders. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Rideau Park real estate is popular for the numerous parks and the serene Elbow River
                views.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Rideau Park was developed way back in 1911 and along with the neighboring Roxboro has
                evolved into a single community. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">All type of homes, including condos, lavish single dwellings to suit different budgets are
                available at Rideau Park. Homes for sale at Rideau Park real estate range from $1 million to $3.8
                million. Condos are available between a price window of $200,000 and $1.5 million.</p>

        </div>
